      • getValue

        String getValue()
        Provides value of the Primitive data objects.
        Returns:
        Returns value of the data object as String if available. Null is provided for Template data objects for which the getDataObjects method should be used instead.

      • getDataObjects

        List<DataObject> getDataObjects()
        Provides inner structure for Template data objects.
        Returns:
        Returns a list of inner data objects if any. Empty list is provided for Primitive data objects.
